### Health check
GET http://localhost:2007/health


# ─── CARD FLOW ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Step 1: Create card → Paylov sends OTP SMS to phoneNumber automatically
# Step 2: User receives OTP → call /cards/confirm
# Step 3: Store the returned cardId from confirm response

### 1. Create Card  (Paylov sends OTP SMS — you do NOT send SMS)
POST http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/cards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_123",
  "cardNumber": "8600123456789012",
  "expireDate": "0126",
  "phoneNumber": "+998901234567"
}


### 2. Confirm Card OTP  → returns final cardId, store it in your DB
POST http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/cards/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardId": "{{cid_from_step_1}}",
  "otp": "123456",
  "cardName": "My Uzcard"
}


### 3. Get Card
GET http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/cards/{{cardId}}


### 4. Delete (deactivate) Card  — marks inactive in DB, no Paylov API call
DELETE http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/cards/{{cardId}}


# ─── DIRECT PAYMENT FLOW (API) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Auth: Bearer access_token only — merchant_id is NOT sent here
# Step 5 → Step 6 → Step 7

### 5. Create Transaction
POST http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_123",
  "amount": 20070,
  "account": {
    "order_id": "ORDER-001",
    "description": "Purchase #001"
  }
}


### 6. Pay (charge the card)
POST http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/transactions/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "{{transactionId_from_step_5}}",
  "cardId": "{{cardId_from_step_2}}",
  "userId": "user_123"
}


### 7. Get Transaction Status
GET http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/transactions?transactionId={{transactionId}}


# ─── CHECKOUT LINK (no card binding) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# merchant_id is read from PAYLOV_MERCHANT_ID env — do NOT pass it in the body
# Returns a URL you redirect the user to for manual payment on Paylov's page

### 8. Generate Checkout Link
POST http://localhost:2007/api/v1/payment/payment-link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 20070,
  "returnUrl": "https://yourapp.com/payment/success",
  "orderId": "ORDER-001"
}
